    <tip>
      <id>528f605f-9994-46b5-8583-cafe006507e4</id>
      <text>Looks like you're building a street samurai. Don't you need a code of honor?</text>
      <chargenonly />
      <required>
        <allof>
          <ess>-1</ess>
          <grouponeof>
            <attribute>
              <name>AGI</name>
              <total>6</total>
            </attribute>
            <cyberwarecategory count="2">Cyberlimbs</cyberwarecategory>
          </grouponeof>
          <grouponeof>
            <skill>
              <name>Automatics</name>
              <val>6</val>
            </skill>
            <skill>
              <name>Pistols</name>
              <val>6</val>
            </skill>
            <skill>
              <name>Longarms</name>
              <val>6</val>
            </skill>
            <skill>
              <name>Archery</name>
              <val>6</val>
            </skill>
            <skill>
              <name>Throwing Weapons</name>
              <val>6</val>
            </skill>
          </grouponeof>
          <grouponeof>
            <skill>
              <name>Blades</name>
              <val>6</val>
            </skill>
            <skill>
              <name>Clubs</name>
              <val>6</val>
            </skill>
            <skill>
              <name>Unarmed Combat</name>
              <val>6</val>
            </skill>
          </grouponeof>
        </allof>
      </required>
      <forbidden>
        <oneof>
          <attribute>
            <name>DEP</name>
            <val>1</val>
          </attribute>
          <attributetotal>
            <attributes>{RES}+{MAG}</attributes>
            <val>2</val>
          </attributetotal>
          <quality>Code of Honor</quality>
          <quality>Code of Honor: Like a Boss</quality>
          <quality>Code of Honor: Avenging Angel</quality>
          <quality>Code of Honor: Black Hat</quality>
        </oneof>
      </forbidden>
    </tip>
    <tip>
      <id>ccaae7df-40ba-4da9-837e-c0df92f07038</id>
      <text>You have enough money to retire with a Low Lifestyle. Keep at it! A nuyen saved is a nuyen earned!</text>
      <careeronly />
      <forbidden>
        <allof>
          <nuyen>500000</nuyen>
        </allof>
      </forbidden>
      <required>
        <allof>
          <nuyen>200000</nuyen>
        </allof>
      </required>
    </tip>
    <tip>
      <id>ff26b01d-1aa4-45ac-8685-0d199e115d1f</id>
      <text>You have enough money to retire with a Medium Lifestyle. 2.5 kids, picket fence AR overlay, loving partner. Is it really worth saving up for that next upgrade?</text>
      <careeronly />
      <forbidden>
        <allof>
          <nuyen>1000000</nuyen>
        </allof>
      </forbidden>
      <required>
        <allof>
          <nuyen>500000</nuyen>
        </allof>
      </required>
    </tip>
    <tip>
      <id>b6da9d78-024d-4516-821c-93ad8207075d</id>
      <text>You have enough money to retire with a Luxury Lifestyle. Molly Millions has nothing on you!</text>
      <careeronly />
      <required>
        <allof>
          <nuyen>100000000</nuyen>
        </allof>
      </required>
    </tip>
    <tip>
      <id>b669df07-528b-4df3-829b-54d095af1791</id>
      <text>Why bother with any other weapon when you can have the Ares Alpha, the last word in automatics! This message brought to you by Ares Macrotechnology.</text>
